{"type": "article", "id": 30356, "title": "还记得小时候玩的魔方吗？有人把它做成了书架｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-31T22:56:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17300, "name": "MOAK Studio"}, {"id": 30848, "name": "Laura Bin"}, {"id": 30849, "name": "Version 22"}, {"id": 30850, "name": "Grey Street Design"}, {"id": 30851, "name": "Anesis"}, {"id": 30852, "name": "Emma Vaneijkeren"}, {"id": 30853, "name": "Laura Klinkenberg"}, {"id": 30854, "name": "Bin Xu"}, {"id": 30855, "name": "Jacob Garcia"}, {"id": 30856, "name": "George Bosnas"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 99, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804171251jJn9A0WzoIbeK5Ma.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>ME dinner set by Emma Vaneijkeren &amp; MOAK Studio</h3><p>食材、餐具，再加上烹饪设备，为户外野餐打包并不是一件轻松的事，而这也启发了荷兰设计师 <a href=\"http://emmavaneijkeren.squarespace.com/info/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Emma Vaneijkeren</a> 和哥伦比亚 <a href=\"http://moakstudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MOAK</a> 工作室在两国的产品设计交流项目 <a href=\"http://mtic-design.nl/project/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MTic</a> 中共同推出了一套多功能的餐具组合 ME。顶部的瓷碗由红石粘土制成，可以用作小型烧烤炉，和白色瓷碗组合后还能用来制作奶酪火锅，无论是户外还是室内聚餐都很适用。野餐毯等杂物可以放进中间的金属结构内，三层组合在一起后由皮带套固定，可以一次性将所需要的东西打包带走。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214114Sn7iZTujUWlfcFhs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214114Lvuz89blGpf6MyFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214115TztQLZibr8CW0mfU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214115y9fVZIQ53B46MzTL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214115YSuqLC0hvEKno4k5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rising balance candleholder by Laura Bin</h3><p>你有没有见过会不断变化的烛台？一侧是燃烧的蜡烛，另一侧是圆柱形的黑色玄武岩，这个像天平一样的设计是阿姆斯特丹设计双人组合 <a href=\"http://www.bindesign.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Laura Bin</a> 的作品，<a href=\"http://www.lauraklinkenberg.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Laura Klinkenberg</a> 和 Bin Xu 两位设计师希望通过它展现出土与火两大元素之间动态关系。随着蜡烛因燃烧而不断减重，纤细的黄铜组件会随之不断调整位置维持平衡。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/the-rising-balance-candleholder/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 85 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040RJziEpu5y0OeUlrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040YvyPpbCfuZnxc82L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040ufsU1AgzJvR4Zxrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040gsmGoY3AvRTJBeKQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040PlFph23BidRAsEtZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214040tTM4zfhU2SwiNGkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nimble by Version 22</h3><p>还在为徒手拆信、快递或是各种贝壳型包装头疼不已吗？来自英国的 <a href=\"http://version22.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Version 22</a> 工作室就设计了一款名为 Nimble 的护指小工具，戴上指尖后只需要简单的动作就能划开材料表面。它的原理在于那块小小的黑色陶瓷刀片，亮黄色的保护套则能够避免手指受到伤害。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/nimble-the-1-finger-wonder-tool-crafts#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 8 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214005gexvPZ8i9GS4qUNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016073121400562xMQdPYqA5tm8UH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214005FdEWxfvU2PT1t5iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.519560\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731214005WX6oKIcg2GN9Ff3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607312140059riJAEoUPTmphMxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fireside Audiobox by Grey Street Design</h3><p>既然水柱能用来展现音乐的变化，火焰是不是也可以？美国俄勒冈州单人设计工作室 Grey Street Design 最近推出了一款火焰音响 <a href=\"http://firesideaudiobox.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fireside Audiobox</a>，铝制的圆柱形燃烧器会随着乐曲的声波和频率喷出对应的橙色火苗，带给人一种奇特的视听感受。燃烧器由一个钢化玻璃罩进行保护，下方则是竹子制成的音箱，整个设备由内置的锂电池进行供电。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/firesideaudiobox/fireside-audiobox-light-your-music-on-fire\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 349 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213934TdeG8V40cRKQ5ian.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213935mncyaeG1R6V3uKOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213934DuAn1LO9XHB5Yxsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213934643Q0by8JlgBarqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213935pznEsQkTBaqK3o5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607312139362aRDNWCUXoKbgxVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sole Stacks by Jacob Garcia</h3><p>对于鞋迷来说，封闭式的柜子的确能够提供一定的收纳空间，但却无法展示自己的珍贵收藏。最近美国波士顿的球鞋设计师 Jacob Garcia 将球鞋的三角形轮廓与鞋架巧妙地结合在一起，推出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://solestacks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sole Stacks</a> 的球鞋收纳系统。它有 6 和 10 层两种高度可选，除了放在地面之外还可以悬挂在墙上，提升了空间的利用率。鞋架的外框和搁板也提供了各种材质和颜色的订制选择，鞋迷能够为自己不同的收藏系列打造充满个性的展示架。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1911512768/sole-stacks-display-and-store-your-shoes-with-love\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 75 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213906UvZuoTcMN4SpgtC1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213906IGAmtPFQX8qRaWE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607312139062OXIVngEcCxZru7j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213907pWfhae9G1EudQvz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213907X6MideaOujcwIESl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rubika B601 by George Bosnas</h3><p>当你第一眼看到空空的 <a href=\"http://anesis.com.gr/en/portfolio/bookcase-rubika/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rubika B601</a> 时，或许还以为它出自某位 3D 绘画师的笔下。它实际上是设计师 George Bosnas 借鉴了鲁比克魔方的造型为希腊品牌 <a href=\"http://anesis.com.gr/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anesis</a> 设计的一款六边形书架，独特的菱形格子不仅可以摆放书籍也可以用来摆放酒瓶、盆栽或是其他装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213843QZGSL3j02MFoW4Jn.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213842kTmtShej2lOo9Eap.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213842LFcf1YWQ8ZyBbnJh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213843ZF3jdHqBu5IRseC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731213842aM8mfqTPVRhBzw2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}